---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/site';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About"
  description="백엔드/인프라 중심의 풀스택 엔지니어. 신뢰성, 성능, 자동화를 추구합니다."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <header class="about-hero reveal">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="profile-image-wrapper">
            <img 
              src="/images/profile.jpg" 
              alt="Profile" 
              class="profile-image"
              onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
            />
            <div class="profile-placeholder">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h1 class="about-title">정원용</h1>
            <p class="about-subtitle">Backend/Infra 중심 풀스택 엔지니어</p>
            <p class="about-tagline">복잡한 문제를 단순하게 해결하고, 자동화를 통해 팀의 생산성을 높입니다.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Quick Links -->
        <div class="quick-links">
          <a href={siteConfig.links.github} class="quick-link card-3d" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>GitHub</span>
          </a>
          <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.author.email}`} class="quick-link card-3d">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/>
              <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Email</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Bento Grid Layout -->
      <div class="bento-grid">
        <!-- About Me -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-large reveal stagger-1">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>소개</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <p>
              <strong>신뢰성 있는 시스템</strong>을 설계하고 구축하는 것을 좋아하는 엔지니어입니다.
              백엔드와 인프라를 중심으로 경험을 쌓았지만, 프론트엔드까지 아우르는 풀스택 역량을 갖추고 있습니다.
            </p>
            <p>
              사용자에게 가치를 전달하는 전체 과정을 이해하고 기여할 수 있는 엔지니어를 지향합니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Experience -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-medium reveal stagger-2">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>경력</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="experience-item">
              <div class="exp-header">
                <h3>(주)더헤르츠</h3>
                <span class="exp-period">2025.11 - 2025.12</span>
              </div>
              <p class="exp-role">Fullstack Engineer</p>
              <ul class="exp-highlights">
                <li>Next.js 기반 통합 브랜드 웹 플랫폼 구축</li>
                <li>AWS (S3, CloudFront) 배포 인프라 구축</li>
                <li>GitHub Actions CI/CD 자동화</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-medium reveal stagger-3">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"></path>
                <path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>학력</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="education-list">
              <div class="edu-item">
                <h3>학점은행제</h3>
                <p class="edu-detail">컴퓨터공학과 학사 수료예정</p>
                <span class="edu-period">2025.03 - 2026.08</span>
              </div>
              <div class="edu-item">
                <h3>인하대학교</h3>
                <p class="edu-detail">산업경영공학과 학사</p>
                <span class="edu-period">2013.03 - 2021.08</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Tech Stack -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-full reveal stagger-4">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>기술 스택</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="tech-grid">
              <div class="tech-category">
                <h3>Backend</h3>
                <div class="tech-tags">
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">Java</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">Spring Boot</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">JPA</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tech-category">
                <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
                <div class="tech-tags">
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">AWS</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">Docker</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Kubernetes</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">GitHub Actions</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tech-category">
                <h3>Database</h3>
                <div class="tech-tags">
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">PostgreSQL</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">MySQL</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Redis</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">MongoDB</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="tech-category">
                <h3>Frontend</h3>
                <div class="tech-tags">
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">React</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag primary">Next.js</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
                  <span class="tech-tag">Vite</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-medium reveal stagger-5">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>가치관</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <ul class="values-list">
              <li>
                <strong>단순함을 추구</strong>
                <span>복잡한 문제를 단순하게 해결하는 것이 좋은 엔지니어링</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>데이터로 판단</strong>
                <span>감보다는 측정과 분석을 통해 의사결정</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>자동화를 사랑</strong>
                <span>반복 작업을 줄이고 창의적인 일에 집중</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>함께 성장</strong>
                <span>지식을 공유하고 팀 전체가 발전하는 환경</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Style -->
        <div class="bento-card bento-medium reveal stagger-6">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-icon">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>일하는 방식</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <ul class="work-list">
              <li>문제의 본질을 먼저 파악하고 효과적인 해결책을 찾습니다</li>
              <li>코드 리뷰를 통해 지식을 공유하고 품질을 높입니다</li>
              <li>문서화와 기록을 중요하게 생각합니다</li>
              <li>작은 단위로 자주 배포하고 빠르게 피드백을 반영합니다</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: var(--space-10) 0 var(--space-20);
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-10);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .profile-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .profile-placeholder {
    display: none;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 3px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .hero-text {
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about-tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Quick Links */
  .quick-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .quick-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-5);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .quick-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  /* Bento Grid */
  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .bento-card {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .bento-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-hover);
  }

  .bento-large {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .bento-medium {
    grid-column: span 1;
  }

  .bento-full {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .card-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .card-header h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-content p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .card-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Experience */
  .experience-item {
    padding: 0;
  }

  .exp-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .exp-header h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .exp-period {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .exp-role {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .exp-highlights {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .exp-highlights li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .exp-highlights li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* Education */
  .education-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .edu-item h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .edu-detail {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .edu-period {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Tech Grid */
  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .tech-category h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tech-tag {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .tech-tag.primary {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: transparent;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Values */
  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .values-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .values-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .values-list li:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .values-list strong {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .values-list span {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* Work List */
  .work-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .work-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
  }

  .work-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bento-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .bento-large,
    .bento-medium,
    .bento-full {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .tech-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-4);
    }

    .about-title {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }

    .profile-image,
    .profile-placeholder {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }

    .quick-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
